and that vibration merely enough to admit of the crosswise interblending of other threads with its own.

10
00:01:22,134 --> 00:01:31,965
This warp seemed necessity, and here, thought I, with my own hand I ply my own shuttle and weave my own destiny into these unalterable threads.

11
00:01:32,125 --> 00:01:40,474
