whence that voice dropped like a wing.

18
00:02:49,736 --> 00:02:54,123
High aloft in the cross-trees was that mad gay header Tashtego.

19
00:02:54,844 --> 00:03:03,499
His body was reaching eagerly forward, his hands stretched out like a wand, and at brief sudden intervals he continued his cries.

20
00:03:03,479 --> 00:03:13,014
To be sure, the same sound was that very moment, perhaps being heard all over the seas, from hundreds of whalemen's lookouts perched as high in the air.

21
00:03:13,636 --> 00:03:30,583
